      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 7
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there, car lovers! Up for grabs is my absolute pride and joy. Honestly, calling this beauty 'clean' is an understatement\u2014it\u2019s more like a time capsule. I\u2019ve babied this ride since day one, keeping it tucked away and polished to a mirror finish. The interior still has that fresh feel, and it drives as smooth as the day it left the lot. It\u2019s a rare find to see one kept in this kind of shape, and I\u2019m looking for a new owner who will appreciate it just as much as I have. Come take a look, let's chat cars, and see why this is the one you\u2019ve been waiting for!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 7
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This is a surgically maintained specimen for the driver who understands mechanical harmony. The powerplant features a precision-mapped ECU curve that maximizes mid-range torque while maintaining rock-solid compression across all cylinders. I've ensured the valvetrain is whisper-quiet with zero lash, and the gearbox provides that sought-after bolt-action engagement with no hint of synchro hesitation. The chassis has been tightened with high-durometer bushings and a corner-balanced coilover setup that delivers telepathic turn-in. Finished with a multi-stage paint correction and a hydrophobic ceramic layer, the exterior depth is unparalleled. This isn't just a car; it's a dialed-in technical achievement ready for the track or the collection. Turn-key, zero-leak, and absolutely sorted.",
      "price": 44500.0,
